sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant B as Browser (SPA)
    participant JS as JavaScript App
    participant API as Server
    participant DB as Database

    U->>B: Type note and click "Save"
    B->>JS: Trigger submit event
    JS->>JS: Prevent default form reload
    JS->>API: POST /new_note_spa (note content as JSON)
    API->>DB: Store new note
    DB-->>API: Success response
    API-->>JS: 201 Created + note data
    JS-->>B: Update notes list in DOM
    B-->>U: Show new note immediately (no page reload)
